Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭也已经近在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哔哔哔…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把腰放低  洗脑光线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哔哔哔…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不知不觉才团结起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副会长  海报似乎快不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我马上拜托印刷厂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副会长  关于后庭的场地划分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个已经完成了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉变得拼命起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢  我试穿了一下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常闪亮啊  真耀眼得让人无法直视
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错呢不错呢  我也要发光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝  你的衣服啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得  这样似乎也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  有没有汗臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得不淋浴没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  要和大叔去吃饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答问题  劣等狗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…不臭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢  还真是拼命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明工作那么忙还每天晚上来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家庭餐厅一起吃饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不认为因为这种程度\N我就会把至今为止的事情全都忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是嘛  那家伙还认识几间好吃的店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微陪陪他也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还什么都没说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  这么早就来接了不是连换衣服的时间都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你家的车么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没在暗地里偷笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  那边在等你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔从那以后真的在加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了想办法取回失去的时间和信赖  十分拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  在加油的不只是大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力地想要回应大叔的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗脑光线  哔哔哔…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚也很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于文化祭的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}职业摔跤秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  文化祭就在明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓起干劲上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  关于化妆的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}Macarons：起源于18世纪法国的一种小圆饼，由蛋清、杏仁粉、糖粉等制成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要请笨蛋吉帮忙  真让人不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就咬牙忍耐一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻笑什么啊  真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦  难得大叔说要来看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就赶紧下定决心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里给我站十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和笨蛋吉谈妥之前别进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦下  那边的高须同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能让下路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然要送我礼物  这不是明摆着有阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌呢笨蛋吉  怎么可能会有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请好好享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人  这不是超有名餐厅卖的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天和父亲去了  想给笨蛋吉礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说连做模特的同伴都难以入手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  赶紧吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  我要在家里和红茶一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上吃吧吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦  我吃就是了  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  这样行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  过去一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  搞什么你  果然有巨大的阴谋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭的职业摔跤秀  一次就好  和我交换角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想演更好的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河竟然会想要演主角…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那家伙的老爸要来看文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想要给他看她的长处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝大致也知道的吧  那家伙的家庭状况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近啊  她老爸想要重结父女的缘分…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊  突然这是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得让大河清醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种爸爸不能相信  必须得告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  要做这么过分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大河的挚友的话不应该为她高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高兴？  我吗？  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被到现在才厚着脸皮跑出来的爸爸欺骗的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么样才能为她高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着朋友受到伤害还笑着看着这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说绝对做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换交换
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样也太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什么都不知道  别擅做主张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河的老爸是个很为女儿着想的好大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见过了还这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高须同学  你和那人见面的时候有好好睁着眼睛看他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那眼睛看清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙…龙儿  小实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握…握手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙…龙儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里  可是我的间隙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  正合适
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  果然这里是我的间隙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝她怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你能对着喜欢的女孩那样大吼大叫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是栉枝不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真让人不敢相信  竟然是能说出那种话的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你对我发牢骚  我也不会温柔地同情你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  回去开始彩排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊  我把好不容易才热闹起来的气氛破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  我会支援你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  和我一起的话就回得去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…  变了呢  果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想改变啊  怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别撒娇了  自己去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会像大河一样和高须同学一直粘在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会成为小实那样成为高须同学闪耀的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过的呢  「对等」…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,订正
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川岛亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:10:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和高须同学在同一条路上  稍微前面一点走着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小龙  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子已经饿扁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近总是回来得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有文化祭的准备没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过一会儿就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  听说大河妹妹要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是  听谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像呢  因为午睡的时候隔壁很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家具全部都处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你好你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  吵吵闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个自称是大河妹妹的爸爸的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是要两个人生活的话  那间公寓太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个自作主张的爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不是吗  突然跑回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你也要说那种话么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…  这不是好事么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父女俩在新的家里重新开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河妹妹不在我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家已经是三口人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要不要  为什么大河妹妹不和泰泰说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一股焦臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「见外」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}注：日语「见外」写作「水臭い」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没回来么  明天都要正式上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔今晚也该替她着想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  大河觉得好的话不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都快要顺利进行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  回来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚要谈些什么啊  还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说我的事  是关于小实的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地去道个歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…觉得我并没有说错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样  不是谁对谁错的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那种事  还有更重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会需要道歉和原谅这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  给我好好去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭的早晨来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来份炒面怎么样  炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}THE·职业摔跤·秀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  排得好长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  怎么办怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点  春田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能冷静  高…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  在玩什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  哎？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么  这条面容炸弹狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我只是觉得昨天给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天要努力演坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从任何方面来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要那种自己也觉得「是不是还不够呢」的程度就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个  好好道过歉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没  还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点的话你  难得的文化祭就不能和小实一起逛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}喔  不愧是栉枝  真合身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}是吗  合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}合适合适
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}穿这个合身的也只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆出这么没出息的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}别这么说嘛  会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  终于要正式上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接待处那边的报告  会场已经八成满了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个样子  说不定还会有站着看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好显眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么  2C职业摔跤演出第一场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝愿顺利成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一发！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2C的职业摔跤超级棒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？很有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说川岛亚美穿着好强大的迷你裙出场的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌中老虎和不良少年高须同学好像超级搞笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个班级里流传的的传说中的秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  超级珍贵的秘密宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班主任的红线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  唯独对那个请不要下手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们应该是2C的伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}怎么可以做这样过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出场了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}有这样的事吗  我的身心已经全部献给老虎大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  掌中老虎大人  请登场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}哔哔哔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎大人请下达指示  这根红线要如何处置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钳…给我钳掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才…咬到舌头了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:15:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬到了咬到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪…给我剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  不要剪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好逼真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  这样的剧本里可没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了  能登
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子军团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把班主任抬去Morgue吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的红线～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morgue是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体安置的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这是何等残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙伴们都被洗脑  我到底该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神灵注视着一切哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战士亚美哟  如果你真的掌握着人心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能解除大家的洗脑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  要开始了  这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不管怎么样都请回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  请努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的重要的  攻击  机～会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世上被称为是最美的人物的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川岛亚美！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我们到底干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚美～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  尽用这些小把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:18:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不…不能原…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅  川岛亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到了  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  今天的高潮部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌中老虎  VS  川岛亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚美  后面后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近得意过头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还去了亚美的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了哦  小不点老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  背抽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再忍一会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换后我会让你做回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  大受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴头套真热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说下次演出啊  应该更…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的茶不…不喝也不要紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只属于你的王子来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么好像都是COSPLAY咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外地都没什么内容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人进出的也很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  副会长还去附近学校做了宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一场还真是不错的盛况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  下场也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吃缎带哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来那薄饼相当美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边上的能给我一口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管吃…吃吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  真是大方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北村  你还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙…龙儿也来一口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到学生会巡逻的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  你们先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北村同学的…  北村同学的吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  差不多该到下一场秀的时间了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:21:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别生气了啊  是你自己塞到我嘴里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  大叔那边有来短信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一直在看手机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是游戏啊  游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待出场时也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  反正还有几场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔来了的话  马上就和川岛换一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事怎么样都好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是好好考虑下小实的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  准主角  太棒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河还是没有…演过一次主角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20\fad(0,1200)}公演结束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就如栉枝所说的  什么都没看清吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话  那样的话我不是多么…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么  迟钝的家伙
